Bed Bath & Beyond Increases Its Full-Year Profit Forecast; Shares Advance

-- B y   C o u r t n e y   D e n t c h
-- 
2011-06-22T20:32:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/bed-bath-beyond-increases-its-full-year-profit-forecast-shares-advance.html
Bed Bath & Beyond Inc. (BBBY)  said earnings
per share this year will rise as much as 20 percent, up from a
previous forecast for as much as a 15 percent gain.  The shares climbed $1.84, or 3.4 percent, to $55.90 at 4:26
p.m. New York time, after the close of regular Nasdaq Stock
Market composite trading.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Courtney Dentch at 
 cdentch1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Robin Ajello at   rajello@bloomberg.net . 